## 5. CRUD Routing Logic

### Frontend Decision Tree

```typescript
const handleSave = async (formData: Partial<Entity>) => {
  try {
    if (selectedEntity.value?.id) {
      // ✅ Has ID → Update (PATCH)
      await updateEntity(selectedEntity.value.id, formData);
    } else {
      // ✅ No ID → Create (POST)
      await createEntity(formData);
    }
    await fetchData();  // Refresh to sync
  } catch (err) {
    error.value = getApiErrorDetail(err);
  }
};
```

